{"tid":958951,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"半程冠軍利物浦 諗定勝利巡遊？","createTime":"2018-12-28T08:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T16:19:40.000Z","uid":7715,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"29cffe32f3e99109b8ce4d27f57ec407ca3cca1f","tid":958951,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:23:24.000Z","msg":"利物浦領先第二名熱刺6分，成為英超今季的半程冠軍，有機會奪得29年來的首個聯賽錦標，不過若現在已計劃勝利巡遊就似乎言之過早。日前有利物浦球迷在球隊所屬地區的利物浦市理事會Twitter上查詢，利物浦的英超聯勝利巡遊會在何時舉行，竟然獲得答覆︰「若利物浦贏得英超冠軍，勝利巡遊會在2019年5月22日星期日舉行」，但留言很快已被刪除，利物浦市理事會Twitter的管理人員及後更留言為出錯道歉，表示目前並沒有勝利巡遊的資料。 <br />\n<br />\n其實紅軍過去不乏奪取英超冠軍的機會，但最後都未竟全功，所以紅軍球迷今次都不願討論球隊奪標的可能性。英國《鏡報》就笑指利物浦現已觸怒了足球命運之神，將會在最後時刻倒下，將冠軍讓予熱刺、曼城或其他球隊，到時利物浦市將會滿是憤怒的利物浦球迷了！"},{"pid":"b6d628d2c166e34ba58dcfa03e4beaa944fe0d9e","tid":958951,"uid":886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdDX1oY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdDX1oY.png&h=cffd65e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd3891861d200de00c24d15376de17cd4516bff","tid":958951,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d628d2c166e34ba58dcfa03e4beaa944fe0d9e","tid":958951,"uid":886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdDX1oY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdDX1oY.png&h=cffd65e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"血小板。。。"},{"pid":"2f49d7e048fdf6186a59c5ce2e8e04f72e5d1abe","tid":9589